# Privacy Policy for ReefKeeper

**Last updated: March 14, 2026**

## Overview

ReefKeeper is a reef tank management app that stores all data locally on your device. We are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what data the app uses and how it is handled.

## Data Collection

**ReefKeeper does not collect, transmit, or share any personal information.**

All data you enter into the app — including tank information, water parameters, livestock records, maintenance logs, equipment, reminders, expenses, photos, and settings — is stored exclusively on your device in a local database.

## Data Storage

- All app data is stored locally on your device using an on-device database.
- No data is sent to external servers, cloud services, or third parties.
- No analytics, tracking tools, or advertising SDKs are used in the app.
- No account creation or sign-in is required to use the app.

## Backup & Restore

- The backup feature creates a local JSON file that you control entirely.
- You choose where to save or share your backup file (Downloads folder, email, cloud storage, etc.).
- ReefKeeper never accesses, reads, or transmits your backup files.
- Importing a backup restores data only to your local device.

## Photos

- Tank photos are stored locally on your device.
- Photos are never uploaded, shared, or transmitted by the app.
- The app accesses your device's photo gallery only when you choose to add a photo.

## Permissions

ReefKeeper requests the following permissions:

- **Notifications**: Used to deliver reminder alerts that you configure. You can disable notifications at any time in your device settings.
- **Storage/Media**: Used for saving backup files to your Downloads folder and accessing photos you choose to add to your tank records.

## Third-Party Services

ReefKeeper does not integrate with any third-party services, analytics platforms, advertising networks, or data processors.

## Children's Privacy

ReefKeeper does not knowingly collect any information from children under the age of 13. The app does not collect information from any user.

## Changes to This Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date. Since no data is collected, changes would only relate to new app features or permissions.

